title: NFL Week 6 Recap (Football 10/15)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by John Breech and Sean Wagner to break down the biggest games from Week 6 of the 2018 NFL season, including the crazy Chiefs-Patriots game, the Buccaneers and Falcons shootout and the Bears overtime gag. Then the guys surprise Ryan Wilson with a call to his South Florida hotel room to talk about the Steelers win over the Bengals and the rest of the Week 6 action. At some point a spirited discussion about Sean McDermott erupts.
